Services
This section covers everything you need to know about our ordering process and return policy.
Q&A
Q: What is the estimated delivery time for my order?
A: We aim to deliver all orders within 3-7 business days, depending on your location. You will receive a tracking number once your order has shipped so you can follow its journey.
Q: Can I cancel my order after I've placed it?
A: Yes, you can cancel your order within 4 hours of placing it. Please contact our support team immediately with your order number to request a cancellation. Once an order has been shipped, it cannot be canceled.
Q: What is your return policy?
A: We offer a hassle-free return policy. You can return any product within 7 days of delivery for a refund or replacement, provided it is unused, in its original packaging, and with all accessories.
Q: My RC toy is damaged or defective. What should I do?
A: If you receive a damaged or defective item, please contact our support team within 48 hours of delivery. We will arrange for a replacement or a full refund after the product has been verified.
Q: Who pays for the return shipping?
A: We will cover the return shipping costs if the item is damaged, defective, or incorrect. For all other returns (e.g., you changed your mind), the customer is responsible for the return shipping fee.
Q: How long does it take to get a refund after a return?
A: Once we receive and inspect the returned item, a refund will be processed to your original payment method within 5-7 business days.
Q: How can I track my order?
A: After your order is confirmed and shipped, you will receive an email with a tracking number and a link to the courier's website. You can use this to track your package's delivery status.
Q: What payment methods do you accept?
A: We accept all major credit and debit cards, as well as net banking and popular digital wallets.
Q: Can I change my delivery address after placing an order?
A: If your order has not yet been shipped, you can contact us to request an address change. However, once the package is with the courier, we cannot guarantee a change of address.
Q: Do you deliver to my location?
A: We offer delivery to most pin codes across the country. To check if we deliver to your area, please enter your pin code on the product page or during checkout.

Pricing & Payments
This section provides details on pricing, payments, and any related charges.
Q&A
Q: Are there any hidden charges?
A: No, the price you see on the product page is the final price. All taxes and delivery charges are included in the total at checkout.
Q: Do you offer a Cash on Delivery (COD) option?
A: Yes, we offer a Cash on Delivery (COD) option for select locations and for orders up to a certain value. You can check if COD is available during the checkout process.
Q: Why was my payment declined?
A: Payments can be declined for a number of reasons, such as incorrect card details, insufficient funds, or a bank-related issue. Please check with your bank or try a different payment method.
Q: Is my payment information secure?
A: Yes, all transactions on our website are encrypted and processed through a secure payment gateway to ensure your information is safe.
Q: Do you offer discounts or promotions?
A: We frequently run special promotions. To stay updated, follow us on social media or subscribe to our newsletter.
Q: Why did the price of an item change after I added it to my cart?
A: Prices are subject to change based on ongoing promotions or stock availability. The final price is reflected at the time of checkout.
Q: Can I get an invoice for my order?
A: Yes, you will receive a digital invoice via email after your order is confirmed and the product is delivered.
Q: What should I do if my payment was successful but the order status isn't updated?
A: Please wait for a few minutes. If the status doesn't change, contact our support team with your transaction details. We will verify the payment and update your order.
Q: Can I use a gift card or a coupon code?
A: Yes, you can apply a valid gift card or coupon code during checkout.
Q: Is there an extra charge for batteries or accessories?
A: All accessories and batteries are sold separately. You can find their prices listed on the respective product pages.


